title: The Last Filling Station
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, International, Western, Asian, Filipino, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. In a resort with no vegan or vegetarian restaurants, this one offers a vegetarian menu with the most choices in town. As of Feb 2016, the main menu lists 6 vegetarian items, of which at least half are vegan or can be made vegan. Other specified choices for breakfast, noodles and rice are also available.
